FLEX:
justify = main-axis
justify-content (flex): all individual children
justify-content (grid): full grid
justify-items (grid): all children within their cells
justify-self (grid): self-alignment (overwrites justify-items)e

align = cross-axis
align-content (flex): for multiple rows/columns
align-items (flex/grid): all individual children within their row/column
align-self (flex): self-alignment (overwrites align-items)

place = justify+align


flex-basis > main-axis size
cross-axis-size > align-self: stretch


MULTI-SIDED-VALUES:
all sides
vertical, horizontal
top, horizontal, bottom
top, right, bottom, left
(mnemonic: clockwise from top with combinations)